    "Corporate-baseline alias map. Loaded by SymbolAliasRegistry under",
    "the project's <project>/_BIM_COORD/symbol_aliases.json — project",
    "entries win by key, project-only keys append.",
    "",
    "Match priority (case-insensitive, first hit wins):",
    "  1. Exact 'FamilyName::TypeName'",
    "  2. Exact 'FamilyName'",
    "  3. Exact 'TypeName'",
    "  4. Glob 'prefix*'",
    "  5. Glob '*substring*'",
    "",
